# 业务连续性计划 (BCP) 流程
# 源: operational-model.md 内联 mermaid

direction: down

classes: {
  crit: { style: { fill: "#ffcdd2"; stroke: "#c62828" } }
}

INC: "事件发生"
P0: "P0 级?" { shape: diamond }
ESC: "5min 内升级" { class: crit }
ASS: "常规响应"
WAR: "指挥室成立\nCTO+SRE+Sec+PM" { class: crit }
ACT: "执行 runbook"
CHK: "SLO 恢复?" { shape: diamond }
ESCL: "升级灾备预案" { class: crit }
MON: "持续监控 24h"
DR: "启动异地/冷备" { class: crit }
PM: "事后复盘"
KB: "沉淀 runbook"

INC -> P0
P0 -> ESC: "是"
P0 -> ASS: "否"
ESC -> WAR
WAR -> ACT
ACT -> CHK
CHK -> ESCL: "否"
CHK -> MON: "是"
ESCL -> DR
DR -> MON
MON -> PM
PM -> KB
